    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those elements in lighting devices, usually cords, ribbons, or tubes of loosely woven, twisted, or braided fibers, that draw fuel to the flame by capillary action.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>De elementen van verlichtingsmiddelen, meestal koorden, linten of hulzen van los geweven, gedraaide of gevlochten vezels, die brandstof naar de vlam voeren door middel van capillaire werking.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
